==English==
===Conjunction===
'''exclusive or'''
  
#(''logic, computing'') A [[connective]] joining two [[predicate]]s A and B that is true when exactly one of A and B is true. Abbreviated ''[[XOR]]''

====Translations====
*Finnish: [[poissulkeva tai]]
*French: [[ou exclusif]]
*Hungarian: [[kizáró vagy]]
*Latin: [[vel#Latin|vel]]

